descp2: {'auto', 'ball_tree', 'kd_tree', 'brute'}, optional Algorithm used to compute the nearest neighbors: - 'ball_tree' will use :class:`BallTree` - 'kd_tree' will use :class:`KDTree` - 'brute' will use a brute-force search. - 'auto' will attempt to decide the most appropriate algorithm based on the values passed to :meth:`fit` method. (default) Note: fitting on sparse input will override the setting of this parameter, using brute force.
